ggest%20year-over-year%20increase%20in%20November%20since%20summer%202021%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Redfin%20report%20released%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMortgage%20rates%20are%20dropping%20due%20to%20easing%20inflation%20and%20investors%20betting%20the%20Fed%20will%20cut%20interest%20rates%20sooner%20than%20expected%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Redfin%20economics%20research%20lead%20Chen%20Zhao%2C%20in%20the%20release.%20%26quot%3BDeclining%20rates%2C%20along%20with%20a%20sizable%20year-over-year%20increase%20in%20new%20listings%2C%20are%20leading%20to%20more%20favorable%20conditions%20for%20some%20buyers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20payments%20have%20dropped%20for%20the%20fifth%20week%20in%20a%20row%2C%20from%20%242%2C739%20in%20October%20to%20%242%2C575%20in%20the%20first%20four%20weeks%20of%20November.%20New%20listings%20were%20up%206%25%20%E2%80%94%20the%20biggest%20uptick%20in%20over%20two%20years%20%E2%80%94%20which%20points%20towards%20an%20easing%20supply%20crunch%20in%20the%20housing%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20buyers%20are%20taking%20note.%20According%20to%20the%20release%2C%20mortgage-purchase%20applications%20are%20up%205%25%20week%20over%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decline%20in%20mortgage%20payments%20stems%20from%20a%20decline%20in%20mortgage%20rates%20which%20have%20been%20stepping%20lower%20from%20their%20peak%20of%208%25%20notched%20in%20October.%20As%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20daily%20average%20for%20the%2030-year%20mortgage%20rate%20was%207.13%25%20%E2%80%94%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%20September.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20market%2C%20which%20has%20been%20tight%20all%20year%2C%20still%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20before%20conditions%20truly%20loosen.%20While%20the%20drop%20in%20mortgage%20payments%20lops%20off%20%24164%20from%20last%20month's%20peak%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20whole%2013%25%20higher%20than%20November%20last%20year.%20And%20the%20home%20prices%20were%20up%20by%204%25%2C%20with%20the%20total%20number%20of%20homes%20for%20sale%20down%207%25%20since%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20confluence%20of%20high%20prices%2C%20high%20interest%20rates%2C%20and%20stubbornly%20low%20inventory%20are%20flash%20frying%20home%20buying%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Jamie%20Cox%2C%20Managing%20Partner%20for%20Harris%20Financial%20Group%2C%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BIf%20rates%20fall%20next%20year%2C%20housing%20will%20snap%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20uptick%20in%20listings%20is%20indeed%20a%20whiff%20of%20hope%20for%20the%20low%20supply%20in%20the%20market%2C%20and%20falling%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20a%20good%20sign%20for%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20advice%20for%20serious%20homebuyers%20is%20to%20compare%20housing%20costs%20to%20recent%20highs%20instead%20of%20long-ago%20lows%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhao%20said%20in%20the%20Redfin%20release.%20%26quot%3BHousing%20costs%20are%20at%20their%20lowest%20level%20in%20three%20months%20and%20it's%20unlikely%20they%20will%20drop%20significantly%20anytime%20soon.%20That%20makes%20it%20a%20relatively%20good%20time%20to%20lock%20in%20a%20rate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-mortgage-rates-fed-rate-cuts-payments-home-listings-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701358580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6568933e86933e8fdb2e4da5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fhousing-market-mortgage-rates-fed-rate-cuts-payments-home-listings-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%20advice%20for%20serious%20homebuyers%20is%20to%20compare%20housing%20costs%20to%20recent%20highs%20instead%20of%20long-ago%20lows%2C%26quot%3B%20Redfin's%20Chen%20Zhao%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asoni%40insider.com%20(Aruni%20Soni)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F