3Cspan%3E%20and%20foreign%20policy-security%20outlook.%20The%20current%20Indian%20government%20has%20aggressively%20pursued%20a%20policy%20of%20narrative%20control%20to%20please%20and%20project%20an%20image%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98global%20moral%20power%E2%80%99%20and%20%3Cem%3EVishwaguru%3C%2Fem%3E%20(world%20leader)%20under%20Modi%20across%20each%20multilateral%20and%20plurilateral%20summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20often%20than%20not%2C%20it%20is%20authoritarian%20countries%20like%20Russia%2C%20China%20or%20North%20Korea%20which%20are%20in%20the%20news%20for%20alleged%20crimes%20conducted%20on%20foreign%20soil%2C%20damaging%20their%20reputation.%20Can%20one%20imagine%20how%20India%E2%80%99s%20intel%20and%20information%20sharing%20architecture%20with%20its%20democratic%20allies%20and%20partners%20may%20be%20disrupted%20after%20an%20episode%20like%20this%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20previous%20article%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findia-g20-economy-world-domestic-outlook%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethis%20author%20argued%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ehow%20India%E2%80%99s%20paradoxical%20world%20outlook%20and%20waning%20moral%20stature%20in%20conduct%20on%20multilateral%20(and%20some%20bilateral)%20issues%2C%20cannot%20be%20enveloped%20nor%20hidden%20in%20some%20%E2%80%98green%20tented%20sheet%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20indictment%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%20hints%20at%20what%20may%20have%20informed%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJustin%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20sensational%20September%202023%20statement%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20there%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20linking%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20the%20murder%20of%20another%20Khalistan%20activist.%20While%20Ottawa%20has%20not%20revealed%20much%20in%20public%20%E2%80%93%20app