its%20global%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emoral%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Estanding.%20In%20India%E2%80%99s%20own%20amoral%2C%20apathetic%20exceptionalism%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20silent%20embrace%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassin%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20and%20his%20(Godse%E2%80%99s)%20ideological%20disposition%2C%20as%20against%20an%20embrace%20of%20Gandhian%20ideals%20of%20peace%20and%20non-violence%20which%20made%20India%20globally%20recognised%20and%20respected%20by%20all%20powers%20across%20the%20globe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20also%20buffoonish%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20policy%20ecosystem%20to%20believe%20it%20enjoys%20an%20undistilled%20faith%20amongst%20the%20(still)%20powerful%20G7%20countries%20if%20the%20tools%20for%20channelising%20instruments%20of%20economic%20integration%20operate%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esans%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20basic%20domestic%20prerequisites%20of%20realised%20social%20cohesion%3B%20a%20safeguarded%20rights-based%20constitutional%20order%2C%20ensured%20by%20the%20separation%20of%20powers.%20India%20can%20hardly%20compromise%20on%20these%20prerequisites%20if%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20playing%20a%20more%20important%20role%20in%20a%20complex%2C%20multi-polar%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-pannun-modi-foreign-policy-national-interest%5C%22%3EFrom%20Nijjar%20to%20Pannun%2C%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Recklessness%20is%20Undermining%20National%20Interest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20West%E2%80%99s%20more%20accommodative%20position%20on%20a%20number%20of%20contested%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20on%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%2C%20the%20Ukraine-Russia%20war%2C%20or%20on%20domestic%20issues%20like%20human%20rights%2C%20minority%20protection%2C%20and%20freedom%20of%20press%20%E2%8