owned.%20The%20thought%20of%20sacrificing%20my%20core%20values%20and%20authenticity%20for%20financial%20success%20made%20me%20hesitant%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20I%20finally%20stepped%20onto%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-nyu-student-study-abroad-program-racism-traveling-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENYU%20campus%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20discovered%20that%20Stern%20%E2%80%94%20while%20distinct%20from%20a%20typical%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaved-money-by-going-community-college-first-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollege%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20was%20not%20the%20intimidating%20battleground%20I%20had%20envisioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%20Stern%2C%20I've%20embraced%20the%20high-energy%2C%20challenging%20environment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20entering%20Stern's%20revolving%20doors%2C%20I%20was%20instantly%20immersed%20in%20an%20unapologetically%20preprofessional%20world.%20The%20air%20buzzed%20with%20energy%20%E2%80%94%20a%20palpable%20pressure%20that%20plunged%20me%20into%20the%20deep%20end%20from%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20everyone%20except%20me%20knew%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20swim.%26quot%3B%20Fresh%20out%20of%20high%20school%2C%20my%20peers%20arrived%20with%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20filled%20with%20internships%20and%20business%20savvy%20that%20would%20make%20many%20graduates%20green%20with%20envy.%20It%20was%20common%20to%20see%20students%20balancing%20demanding%20internships%20with%20the%20rigorous%20academic%20load%20of%20their%20first%20semester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20essence%20of%20Stern%2C%20however%2C%20was%20unveiled%20to%20me%20in%20the%20first%20week%20through%20its%20clubs.%20These%20are%20not%20mere%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-applications-advice-admissions-expert-apply-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextracurricular%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20they%20are%20the%20coveted%20keys%20to%20networks%20of%20mentorship%20and%20recruitment%20%E2%80%94%20the%20holy%20grail%20for%20high-achieving%20students.%20Yet%20securing%20a%20spot%20in%20these%20clubs%20is%20no%20cakewalk%2C%20with%20some%20receiving%20over%20300%20applications%20for%20fewer%20than%2010%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20environment%2C%20as%20I%20have%20experienced%2C%20is%20a%20double-edged%20sword.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20it%20can%20be%20overwhelming%20and%20disheartening%2C%20especially%20when%20I%20find%20myself%20trailing%20behind%20my%20peers.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20has%20fueled%20my%20relentless%20drive%20to%20excel%2C%20to%20achieve%20more%2C%20and%20to%20continually%20better%20myself.%20In%20my%20time%20at%20Stern%2C%20I%20have%20grappled%20with%20both%20these%20sentiments.%20However%2C%20I%20have%20learned%20to%20embrace%20the%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20discovered%20the%20reality%20at%20Stern%20contrasts%20sharply%20with%20the%20stereotypes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20popular%20belief%2C%20the%20stereotypes%20about%20Stern%20students%20are%20just%20that%20%E2%80%94%20stereotypes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20people%20who%20seem%20to%20fit%20that%20typical%20%26quot%3Bcutthroat%26quot%3B%20mold.%20But%20these%20few%20do%20not%20fully%20represent%20the%20vibrant%20and%20diverse%20community%20that%20makes%20Stern%20special.%20Unfortunately%2C%20those%20people%20tend%20to%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20the%20many%20incredible%20experiences%20that%20students%2C%20including%20myself%2C%20have%20at%20Stern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heart%20and%20soul%20of%20the%20school%20are%20far%20more%20inspiring.%20Most%20of%20my%20peers%20are%20not%20just%20incredibly%20driven%20but%20also%20remarkably%20humble%20and%20down-to-earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20meeting%20hundreds%20of%20st