he%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20exit%20polls%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20also%20showed%20a%20neck-and-neck%20fight%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%2C%20again%20contradicting%20previous%20opinion%20polls%20that%20showed%20a%20comfortable%20victory%20for%20the%20incumbent%20Congress.%20The%20Axis%20India%20Today%20poll%20gave%20a%20slight%20edge%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20too%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20are%20engaged%20in%20a%20close%20battle%2C%20the%20polls%20show.%20However%20Axis%20India%20Today%20poll%20predicted%20a%20landslide%20victory%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20may%20shock%20the%20BRS%20and%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%2C%20some%20polls%20showed%20while%20others%20predicted%20a%20close%20contest.%20The%20BJP%20could%20play%20spoilsport%20if%20it%20splits%20the%20anti-incumbency%20role%2C%20while%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%E2%80%99s%20MIM%20will%20throw%20its%20numbers%20behind%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mizoram%2C%20the%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Zoramthanga%20is%20in%20a%20close%20battle%20with%20fellow%20regional%20player%20Zoram%20Nationalist%20Party%20(ZNF).%20The%20Congress%20may%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20outcome%20if%20a%20hung%20assembly%20is%20elected%20while%20the%20BJP%20may%20fail%20to%20make%20any%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERajasthan%20(Majority%20mark%3A%20100)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20width%3D%5C%22565%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EBJP%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3ECongress%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EOthers%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EIndia%20Today-Axis%20My%20India%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E80-100%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E86-106%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E8-16%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3EABP%20News-C%20Voter%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E94-114%3C