%E2%80%99s%20dominant%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20spectacular%20electoral%20turnaround%2C%20the%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20has%20gained%20huge%20momentum%2C%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20it%20even%20defeating%20the%20BRS%20headed%20by%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20in%20the%20elections%20being%20held%20on%20November%2030.%20Very%20surprisingly%2C%20the%20BJP%20gone%20out%20of%20reckoning%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20secure%20a%20distant%20third%20or%20fourth%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20has%20taken%20place%20following%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20Bharat%20Jod%20Yatra%20and%20the%20decisive%20victory%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20elections%20held%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20Unlike%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20a%20natural%20party%20in%20Telangana%20with%20fairly%20deep%20roots%20across%20the%20state%20even%20before%20it%20was%20carved%20out%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20by%20the%20party%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%20Sympathy%20for%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20for%20having%20created%20Telangana%20is%20now%20palpable%20and%20people%20feel%20that%20the%20KCR-led%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20(now%20BRS)%20has%20taken%20disproportionate%20credit%20and%20acquired%20power%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20local%20leaders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20campaign%20in%20Telangana%20is%20being%20spearheaded%20by%20its%20state%20chief%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20entirely%20depending%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Bereft%20of%20local%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20the%20rank%20and%20file%20of%20the%20party%20was%20perplexed%20when%20its%20popular%20OBC%20leader%2C%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20was%20removed%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20and%20G.%20Krishna%20Reddy%20was%20appointed%20in%20his%20place.%20Such%20a%20decision%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leaders%20is%20a%20replication%20of%20what%20it%20did%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%20regional%20leaders%20were%20sidelined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20306px)%2085vw%2C%20306px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22306%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22253%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20estimated%20itself%20as%20the%20main%20challenger%20to%20the%20BRS%20and%20stridently%20criticised%20the%20KCR%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20indulging%20in%20massive%20corruption.%20OBCs%20constitute%2050%25%20of%20the%20Telangana%20population%20and%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20that%20on%20forming%20government%2C%20he%20would%20appoint%20an%20OBC%20leader%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20sounded%20empty.%20He%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20BJP%20after%20assuming%20power%20would%20scrap%204%25%20reservation%20for%20Muslims%20and%20allot%20that%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20It%20brought%20back%20memories%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20rescinding%20reservation%20for%20Muslims.%20Eventually%2C%20it%20lost%20elections%20to%20the%20Congress%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindutva%20strategy%20has%20been%20deployed%20by%20the%20party%20in%20Telangana%20where%20there%20is%20no%20history%20of%20people%20getting%20mobilised%20on%20religious%20lines%20for%20electoral%20purposes.%20Shah%20also%20promised%20free%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(viewing)%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20being%20inaugurated%20in%20January%202024%20and%20many%20BJP%20leaders%20gave%20assurances%20of%20changing%20the%20name%20of%20Hyderabad%20to%20Bhagyanagar.%20Such%20statements%20never%20assumed%20importance%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul%E2%80%99s%20accusations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20having%20deep%20dealings%20with%20the%20BRS%2C%20which%20he%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98BJP%20Rishtedar%20Samiti%E2%80%99.%20He%20also%20hurled%20similar%20accusations%20against%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Musilmeen%20(AIMIM)%20and%20its%20leader%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20BRS.%20AIMIM%20contests%20only%20in%20nine%20seats%20in%20Telangana%20even%20as%2013%25%20of%20its%20population%20are%20Muslims.%20In%20other%20states%20like%20Bihar%2C%20it%20fields%20its%20candidates%20in%20dozens%20of%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EModiji%20ke%20hai%20do%20yaar%2C%20Owaisi%20aur%20KCR%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20gained%20traction%20among%20the%20Muslims%20of%20Telangana.%20KCR%20engaging%20only%20with%20AIMIM%20to%20discuss%20matters%20concerning%20minorities%20angered%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20and%20Tablighi%20Jamat%2C%20which%20are%20now%20supporting%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Congress%20candidates.%20The%20high-pitch%20campaign%20of%20the%20Congress%20that%20AIMIM%20in%20collaboration%20with%20BRS%20has%20ended%20up%20benefitting%20BJP%20seems%20to%20have%20convinced%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20Telangana%20Votes%2C%20Close%20Fight%20Expected%20Between%20Nervous%20BRS%20and%20Resurgent%20Congress%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-voting-day-close-fight-brs-congress%5C%22%3EAs%20Telangana%20Votes%2C%20Close%20Fight%20Expected%20Between%20Nervous%20BRS%20and%20Resurgent%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20for%20a%20three-cornered%20contest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20tried%20in%20vain%20to%20make%20the%20electoral%20battle%20a%20three-cornered%20contest%2C%20to%20keep%20the%20Congress%20away%20from%20power.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20attacked%20the%20BRS%20to%20take%20steam%20out%20of%20the%20Congress%20campaign%20that%20BJP%20is%20part%20of%20the%20BRS%20and%20AIMIM%20strategy%20for%20securing%20power%20in%20Telangana.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20that%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20took%20no%20action%20against%20KCR%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20corruption%20charges%20hurled%20by%20the%20BJP%20against%20him%20generated%20an%20impression%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20soft%20on%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Y.%20Rajsekhar%20Reddy%20who%20interacted%20with%20people%20by%20organising%20Praja%20Darbars%20regularly%2C%20neither%20KCR%20nor%20his%20MLAs%20did%20anything%20like%20that%20and%20so%20mounting%20anti-incumbency%20created%20fertile%20ground%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20scale%20up%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K%20R%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701343813000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29081618%2FGABNAgRa8AAQtyw.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-resurgent-congress-in-telangana-and-the-challenges-for-brs-and-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rise%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20has%20taken%20place%20following%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20the%20deci