20for%20Justice%E2%80%99%20NGO%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20filings%20charged%20Indian%20resident%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20had%20allegedly%20been%20the%20go-between%20between%20the%20Indian%20government%20official%20(%E2%80%98CC-1%E2%80%99)%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98criminal%20associate%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20%E2%80%98hitman%E2%80%99%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20were%20actually%20working%20for%20US%20law%20enforcement%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20post-indictment%20reaction%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20the%20case%20against%20an%20individual%20that%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20a%20US%20court%2C%20allegedly%20linking%20him%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%2C%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20We%20have%20said%2C%20let%20me%20reiterate%2C%20that%20this%20is%20also%20contrary%20to%20government%20policy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20India%E2%80%99s%20characterisation%20of%20the%20US%20concerns%20as%20being%20related%20to%20criminal%20activity.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20nexus%20between%20organised%20crime%2C%20trafficking%2C%20gunrunning%20and%20extremists%20at%20an%20international%20level%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%20for%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20and%20organisations%20to%20consider%20and%20it%20is%20for%20that%20reason%20that%20a%20high-level%20inquiry%20committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20and%20we%20will%20be%20guided%20by%20its%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bagchi%20said%20at%20a%20media%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20had%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20just%20ahead%20of%20release%20of%20the%20fresh%20indictment%2C%20that%20India%20had%20set%20up%20an%20inquiry%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20US%20%E2%80%98plot%E2%80%99%20on%20November%2018.%20The%20government%20had%20not%20spoken%20of%20the%20committee%20when%20the%20US%20%E2%80%98concerns%E2%80%99%20were%20first%20reported%20by%20the%20media%20%E2%80%93%20and%20then%20confirmed%20by%20the%20White%20House%20%E2%80%93%20on%20November%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20have%20informed%20earlier%2C%20during%20the%20course%20of%20discussions%20with%20the%20US%20on%20bilateral%20security%20cooperation%2C%20the%20US%20side%20shared%20some%20inputs%20pertaining%20to%20nexus%20between%20organised%20criminals%2C%20gun%20runners%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnecessary%20follow-up%20action%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20taken%20based%20on%20the%20Enquiry%20Committee%E2%80%99s%20follow-up%2C%20Bagchi%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20share%20any%20further%20information%20on%20such%20security%20matters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrasting%20India%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20concerns%20raised%20by%20US%20and%20Canada%20about%20targeting%20of%20their%20citizens%2C%20Bagchi%20continued%20with%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20tough%20stance%20against%20Ottawa.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20so%20far%20as%20Canada%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20have%20said%20that%20they%20have%20consistently%20given%20space%20to%20anti-India%20extremists%20and%20that%20is%20actually%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20issue.%20Our%20diplomatic%20representatives%20in%20Canada%20have%20borne%20the%20brunt%20of%20this.%20So%2C%20we%20expect%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%20to%20live%20up%20to%20its%20obligations%20under%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations.%20We%20have%20also%20seen%20interference%20by%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20our%20internal%20affairs%20and%20that%20is%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20filed%20by%20US%20federal%20prosecutor%20clearly%20indicated%20that%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20had%20been%20aware%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98big%20target%E2%80%99%20in%20Canada%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20June%2018%2C%20following%20the%20shooting%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20in%20Canada%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpr%2Fus-attorney-announces-charges-connection-foiled-plot-assassinate-us-citizen-new-york%5C%22%3Ethe%20indictment%20stated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CCC-1%20sent%20GUPTA%20a%20video%20clip%20showing%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20bloody%20body%20slumped%20in%20his%20vehicle%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20significant%20point%20in%20the%20court%20filing%20as%20it%20indicated%20that%20US%20authorities%20had%20obtained%20electronic%20communications%20that%20linked%20the%20Indian%20government%20official%20directly%20to%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20made%20this%20claim%20of%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20September%20this%20year%2C%20which%20New%20Delhi%20had%20instantly%20dismissed.%20The%20Union%20government%20took%20subsequent%20steps%20that%20led%20to%2041%20Canadian%20diplomats%20leaving%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701337983000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22182025%2Fdownload-11.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-court-filing-that-links-assassination-attempt-to-indian-official-matter-of-concern-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20the%20case%20against%20an%20individual%20that%20has%20been%20filed%20in%20a%20US%20court%2C%20allegedly%20linking%20him%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%2C%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20We%20have%20said%2C%20let%20me%20reiterate%2C%20that%20this%20is%20also%20contrary%20to%20government%20policy.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-court-filing-that-links-assassination-attempt-to-indian-official-matter-of-concern-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%