-sends-condolences-to-biden-over-kissingers-death%2Famp_articleshow%2F105620458.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRohit%20And%20Virat%20Were%20Crying%26quot%3B%3A%20Ashwin's%20Big%20Revelation%20On%20WC%20Heartbreak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team%20spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20recalled%20the%20heartbreaking%20scenes%20following%20India's%20defeat%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20against%20Australia.%20India%20were%20unbeaten%20in%20the%20competition%20going%20into%20the%20summit%20clash%20but%20were%20completely%20outplayed%20by%20Australia%20who%20rode%20brilliant%20performances%20from%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Travis%20Head%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F62477-travis-michael-head-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETravis%20Head%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20bowlers%20to%20claim%20a%20record-extending%20sixth%20World%20Cup%20title.%20In%20a%20recent%20interaction%2C%20Ashwin%20said%20that%20both%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20ended%20up%20in%20tears%20after%20the%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20we%20felt%20the%20pain.%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20were%20crying.%20Seeing%20that%20it%20felt%20bad.%20Anyways%2C%20not%20meant%20to%20be.%20This%20team%20was%20an%20experienced%20team.%20Everybody%20knew%20what%20to%20do.%20And%20then%2C%20it%20was%20professional.%20Everybody%20knew%20their%20routines%2C%20warm-ups.%20I%20think%20two%20natural%20leaders%20gave%20the%20team%20the%20space%20to%20do%20these%20two%20(%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit)%20and%20created%20a%20vibe%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ashwin%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20India%20ended%20as%20runners-up%20in%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20Rohit%20received%20a%20lot%20of%20praise%20for%20his%20explosive%20batting%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20order%20and%20his%20captaincy.%20Ashwin%20praised%20Rohit%20as%20someone%20who%20understands%20all%20the%20other%20players%20and%20explained%20that%20he%20puts%20extra%20effort%20to%20know%20more%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20everybody%20will%20tell%20you%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20captains.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20an%20outstanding%20person.%20He%20understands%20every%20single%20person%20in%20the%20team%2C%20he%20knows%20what%20each%20one%20of%20us%20likes%20and%20dislikes.%20He%20has%20a%20great%20understanding.%20He%20puts%20in%20the%20effort%20to%20know%20each%20member%20personally%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0Ashwin%20made%20an%20interesting%20observation%20regarding%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20and%20Mumbai%20Indians%20-%20the%20two%20most%20successful%20team%20in%20IPL%20history%20-%20and%20their%20philosophy%20on%20players%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrading%20so%20many%20players%20or%20releasing%20so%20many%20players%20is%20not%20a%20well-known%20practice%20so%20far%20in%20the%20IPL.%20Because%20if%20you%20look%20at%20these%20IPL%20teams%20and%20talk%20to%20them%2C%20especially%20with%20Mumbai%20Indians%20and%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20trend.%20They%20have%20never%20given%20players%2C%20they%20have%20only%20taken%20players.%20And%20they%20have%20five%20titles%20each.%20That's%20a%20proper%20platform%20that%20they%20have%20built%20their%20franchise%20on%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravi