mediately%20liked%20each%20other.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20of%20courtship%2C%20we%20moved%20in%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maya%20about%20their%20meeting%20around%20nine%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20our%20family%20and%20society%20did%20not%20accept%20us.%20We%20then%20moved%20to%20Kathmandu.%20Although%20we%20got%20married%20in%20a%20temple%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20our%20marriage%20was%20not%20legally%20recognised.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDordi%20Rural%20Municipality%20chairman%20Yuvaraj%20Adhikari%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kathmandu%20Post%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20registration%20request%20had%20been%20filed%20a%20week%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20marriage%20has%20been%20registered%20at%20the%20ward%20office%20after%20the%20Department%20of%20National%20ID%20and%20Civil%20Registration%20instructed%20it%20to%20register%20the%20marriage%20in%20the%20temporary%20record%20as%20per%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20interim%20order%20until%20the%20formulation%20of%20a%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adhikari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20this%20year%2C%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20passed%20an%20interim%20order%20saying%20same-sex%20couples%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20register%20their%20marriages%20while%20a%20final%20decision%20is%20made%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERights%20activists%20have%20welcomed%20Surendra%20and%20Maya%E2%80%99s%20marriage%20registration.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20historic%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sunil%20Babu%20Pant%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Blue%20Diamond%20Society%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fnepal-registers-first-same-sex-marriage-historic-say-activists-2023-11-29%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20will%20open%20the%20door%20for%20them%20to%20jointly%20open%20bank%20accounts%2C%20own%20and%20transfer%20property%20like%20just%20any%20other%20couples.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701319908000%2C%22visual%22%3A%2