mmon%20or%20customary%20or%20international%20law%2C%20including%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20murder%2C%20kidnap%2C%20and%20torture%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20impact%20on%20American%20politics%2C%20too%2C%20has%20been%20questioned%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20Thomas%20Meany%20writing%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fmagazine%2F2020%2F05%2F18%2Fthe-myth-of-henry-kissinger%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Yorker%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20a%20far%20less%20remarkable%20figure%20that%20his%20supporters%2C%20critics%20and%20he%20himself%20believed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKissinger%2C%20however%2C%20is%20credited%20with%20engaging%20with%20West%20Asia%20to%20end%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20War%2C%20and%20negotiating%20the%20Paris%20Peace%20Accords%2C%20which%20ended%20American%20involvement%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20won%20a%20Nobel%20Prize.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhenry-kissinger-american-diplomat-nobel-winner-dead-100-2023-11-30%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20noted%20that%20Kissinger%20had%20been%20active%20with%20meetings%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20writing%20a%20book%20on%20leadership%20styles%2C%20and%20testifying%20before%20a%20Senate%20committee%20about%20the%20nuclear%20threat%20posed%20by%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20this%20year%2C%20he%20made%20a%20surprise%20visit%20to%20Beijing%20and%20met%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhenry-kissinger-dies-at-100%2Fa-67590670%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701313955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F30084130%2FUntitled-design-10-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhenry-kissinger-dies-at-100%22%2C