will%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20across%2035%2C655%20polling%20stations%20in%20the%20state.%20As%20many%20as%202%2C290%20contestants%20are%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20the%20results%20of%20which%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20December%203%2C%20along%20with%20those%20in%20four%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20picture%20that%20has%20emerged%20from%20the%20southern%20state%20is%20that%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20straight%20contest%20between%20seemingly%20nervous%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20and%20a%20resurgent%20Congress%20party.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20going%20by%20various%20surveys%2C%20could%20well%20emerge%20as%20the%20kingmaker%20by%20eating%20into%20the%20anti-BRS%20vote.%20The%20All%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%2C%20like%20always%2C%20could%20well%20be%20on%20its%20way%20to%20retaining%20its%20base%20in%20the%20Old%20City%20of%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20306px)%2085vw%2C%20306px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22306%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22252%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20we%20inched%20closer%20to%20the%20election%20date%2C%20pollsters%20have%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20call%20the%20election%20in%20favour%20of%20any%20party.%20They%20expect%20a%20close%20fight%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20Congress.%20Some%20surveys%20even%20do%20not%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20hung%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20nervous%20BRS%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%2C%20which%20claims%20the%20sole%20credit%20for%20achieving%20statehood%20in%202014%2C%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%20nearly%2010%20years.%20With%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20it%20has%20rolled%20out%20a%20slew%20of%20welfare%20measures%20and%20undertaken%20a%20number%20of%20development%20initiatives.%20According%20to%20BRS%2C%20it%20has%20been%20able%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20positive%20turnaround%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20through%20equal%20thrust%20on%20welfare%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20announcing%20its%20candidates%20almost%20three%20months%20back%20in%20August%2C%20the%20BRS%20was%20the%20first%20to%20hit%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20way%20ahead%20of%20others.%20Confident%20of%20winning%20a%20third%20term%2C%20the%20party%20has%20repeated%20almost%20all%20of%20its%20sitting%20MLAs%2C%20except%20for%20seven%20seats.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20this%20election%20season%20has%20been%20around%20welfare%20schemes%20as%20well%20as%20%E2%80%98successes%E2%80%99%20the%20state%20has%20seen%20in%20the%20power%20and%20irrigation%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20the%20party%20has%20come%20under%20severe%20criticism%20from%20those%20who%20have%20been%20left%20out%20of%20welfare%20schemes.%20Welfare%20schemes%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20could%20prove%20counterproductive%20for%20the%20BRS%20given%20that%20there%20are%20a%20large%20number%20who%20are%20eligible%20yet%20have%20been%20left%20out.%20This%20has%20become%20particularly%20evident%20in%20schemes%20such%20as%20Dalit%20Bandhu%20and%20double-bedroom%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20criticism%20against%20BRS%20has%20been%20the%20perceived%20vice-grip%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20family%20holds%20on%20the%20levers%20of%20administration%20in%20the%20state%20and%20its%20alleged%20corruption.%20Many%20of%20the%20BRS%20MLAs%20are%20also%20accused%20of%20corruption%20in%20their%20constituencies.%20People%20on%20the%20ground%20allege%20that%20ruling%20party%20MLAs%20have%20been%20prioritising%20their%20cronies%20in%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWidespread%20anger%20among%20unemployed%20youth%20in%20the%20state%20is%20palpable%2C%20and%20joblessness%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20key%20poll%20issue.%20Paper%20leaks%20during%20the%20conduct%20of%20recruitment%20exams%20and%20failure%20to%20fill%20vacancies%20in%20government%20departments%20have%20most%20youth%20disappointed%20with%20the%20KCR%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perception%20of%20BRS%20being%20in%20a%20tacit%20understanding%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20the%20AIMIM%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20could%20work%20against%20it%20among%20the%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20minorities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20resurgent%20Congress%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20down%20and%20out%20about%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20has%20made%20a%20surprising%20comeback.%20Since%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%20in%20May%2C%20cadres%20and%20leaders%20in%20Telangana%20have%20received%20new%20vigour%20to%20go%20to%20the%20hustings.%20Besides%20a%20morale%20boost%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20victory%20has%20helped%20the%20party%20to%20strengthen%20its%20financial%20and%20organisational%20muscle%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686533%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20Mallu%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20among%20others.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40INCIndia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decline%20following%20the%20removal%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-cracks-appearing-in-bjps-telangana-unit-after-the-karnataka-debacle%5C%22%3EBandi%20Sanjay%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20Telangana%20unit%20chief%20in%20July%20this%20year%20is%20also%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20Congress.%20The%20loss%20of%20momentum%20for%20the%20BJP%20has%20helped%20Congress%20to%20successfully%20drive%20home%20the%20point%20that%20only%20Congress%20can%20dethrone%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20messaging%20has%20been%20around%20two%20planks%3A%20one%2C%20on%20%3Cem%3Emaarpu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(change)%2C%20and%20two%2C%20by%20projecting%20itself%20as%20Telangana%20%3Cem%3Eichchina%3C%2Fem%3E%20party%20(the%20party%20that%20granted%20statehood).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20also%20seems%20to%20have%20worked%20in%20developing%20a%20positive%20perception%20of%20itself.%20On%20the%20lines%20of%20its%20Karnataka%20manifesto%2C%20the%20party%20has%20announced%20six%20%E2%80%98guarantees%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20voters%20of%20Telangana.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20BRS%2C%20aware%20of%20the%20damage%20potential%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fbrs-attempts-to-trump-congress-manifesto-with-few-more-novel-sops%2Farticle67424024.ece%5C%22%3Esought%20to%20outshine%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0through%20its%20own%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20is%20hopeful%20of%20support%20from%C2%A0youth%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Ftelanganas-exam-hub-trials-and-tribulations-of-job-aspirants-9033684%2F%5C%22%3Egovernment%20job%20aspirants%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20those%20left%20out%20of%20welfare%20schemes%3B%20and%20government%20employees%20who%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20long%20for%20interim%20relief%2C%20restoration%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%2C%20and%20Pay%20Revision%20Commission%20(PRC).%20Additionally%2C%20both%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20minorities%20could%20also%20rally%20behind%20the%20Congress%20due%20to%20its%20effective%20messaging%20that%20the%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20are%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%20faces%20a%20challenge%20on%20two%20fronts%3A%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20effective%20poll%20management%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20possible%20role%20as%20a%20spoilsport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKingmaker%20BJP%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20fortunes%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months%20have%20diminished%20drastically.%20The%20momentum%20it%20had%20built%20with%20victories%20in%20multiple%20bypolls%20and%20its%20stellar%20performance%20in%20the%20election%20to%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC)%20had%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20perception%20that%20it%20was%20the%20principal%20challenger%20to%20the%20incumbent%20BRS.%20However%2C%20the%20easing%20out%20of%20Sanjay%20as%20the%20state%20party%20chief%2C%20factionalism%20in%20the%20state%20leadership%2C%20and%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20central%20leadership%20is%20soft%20on%20the%20BRS%20have%20resulted%20in%20its%20momentum%20being%20fizzled%20out.%20Various%20surveys%20indicate%20that%20it%20could%20emerge%20as%20a%20distant%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20party%20is%20hopeful%20of%20giving%20a%20tough%20fight%20in%20several%20constituencies%2C%20thereby%20affecting%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%20In%20particular%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20face%20a%20stiff%20fight%20for%20anti-BRS%20votes%20in%20about%2020%20seats%2C%20including%20in%20Korutla%2C%20LB%20Nagar%2C%20Bodhan%2C%20Kamareddy%2C%20Nirmal%2C%20Maheshwaram%2C%20and%20in%20a%20few%20handful%20of%20seats%20of%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC).%20With%20a%20hung%20assembly%20not%20ruled%20out%2C%20the%20BJP%20believes%20that%20it%20would%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20kingmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701307848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29221132%2FEffect-4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-voting-day-close-fight-brs-congress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20BRS%20and%20Congress%20are%20the%20main%20contenders%2C%20the%20BJP%20could%20well%20emerge%20as%20the%20kingmaker%20by%20eating%20into%20the%20anti-BRS%20vote.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-voting-day-close-fight-brs-congress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Major%20snowstorm%20spawns%20travel%20chaos%20in%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701305472000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F61D8%2Fproduction%2F_131884052_p0gwrv35.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67573077%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Nor'easter%20storm%20hit%20several%20states%20in%20the%20US%20with%20heavy%20winds%20and%20snow%2C%20creating%20a%20winter%20wonderland.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A