%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FKathirimalai-1-1700489624-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334539%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKathirimalai%20has%20been%20connected%20with%20a%205GHz%20Wi-Fi%20network%20to%20provide%20telemedicine%20and%20tele-education%20services%20to%20tribal%20residents.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20trekking%20back%20from%20the%20hamlet%2C%20the%20officer%20decided%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20woes%20with%20an%20effective%20solution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20looking%20for%20solutions%20once%20the%20problem%20was%20identified.%20We%20did%20not%20intend%20to%20establish%20a%20new%20brick-and-mortar%20structure%20there.%20We%20wanted%20to%20utilise%20the%20resources%20that%20were%20already%20available%20(such%20as%20solar%20power).%20After%20brainstorming%20for%20solutions%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20introduce%20technology%20and%20initiate%20a%20tele-facilitation%20service%20in%20the%20remote%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202022%2C%20Krishnanunni%20launched%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPunnagai%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(meaning%20smile%20in%20Tamil)%20project%20that%20connected%20Kathirimalai%20with%20a%20high-speed%205GHz%20Wi-Fi%20network%20to%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316871%2Ffriends-launch-digiqure-teleconsultation-startup-affordable-rural-healthcare-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etele-medicine%20facilities%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20tele-education%2